        "title": "refactor: extract gateway client package",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Extract gateway protocol sources into `packages/gateway-protocol` and gateway client/runtime helpers into `packages/gateway-client`.\n- Keep `src/gateway/client.ts` as the OpenClaw host wrapper that injects signing, logging redaction, proxy bypass, and host-specific gateway dependencies.\n- Add root build, test, CI-scope, CodeQL, Knip, watcher, CODEOWNERS, and docs routing for the new packages.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: gateway client/protocol package extraction without changing the public OpenClaw gateway client contract.\nReal environment tested: local macOS source checkout on the rebased PR branch; GitHub Actions started for head `b6f4d6a9d94de3d698a88eedd0874f07bcf28bca`.\nExact steps or command run after this patch:\n\n```sh\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.cwd-split.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/gateway/client.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/index.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/native-protocol-levels.guard.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/primitives.secretref.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -b tsconfig.core.json\nOPENCLAW_LOCAL_CHECK=0 pnpm deadcode:dependencies\ngit diff --check\n```\n\nEvidence after fix: focused embedded-runner test passed 1 file / 2 tests; focused gateway/protocol Vitest passed 8 files / 190 tests; core tsgo passed; dependency deadcode check passed; `git diff --check` passed.\nObserved result after fix: gateway protocol types resolve from `packages/gateway-protocol`, gateway client host checks use `ipaddr.js` instead of hand-rolled IPv6 parsing, and the root gateway client wrapper preserves existing OpenClaw host behavior.\nWhat was not tested: no live gateway/device pairing scenario was run.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.cwd-split.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/gateway/client.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/index.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/native-protocol-levels.guard.test.ts packages/gateway-protocol/src/primitives.secretref.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -b tsconfig.core.json`\n- `OPENCLAW_LOCAL_CHECK=0 pnpm deadcode:dependencies`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main` running for final closeout on the pushed head\n",
